casebody.data:
No. 10-7236. Gary Steven Calhoun, Petitioner v. California. 562 U.S. 1107, 131 S. Ct. 850,

178 L. Ed. 2d 554,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 9658. December 13, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma paup-*555eris denied. Petitioner is allowed until January 3, 2011, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
